{"tid":869646,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【走塑佬】飲管可以用咩代替","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T07:51:56.000Z","uid":198810,"like":49,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"56cfd24bc8ff851498cfaaac7d22c89c76ebc532","tid":869646,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"環保撚成日話要保護<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">海龜</span></strong>唔好再吸到啲飲管<br />\n又話咩一支塑膠飲管需要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">400至500年</span></strong>先可以被分解<br />\n但係有冇諗過其實點解<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">飲管</span></strong>會被發明出嚟<br />\n最重要就係可以保護牙齒<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">費事飲甜嘢會蛀牙</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁究竟有咩物料可以環保之餘又可以舒舒服服咁飲嘢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1735524/org/76df3a4f202f806f40eef46fa4e63065.jpg/V-8wlDtgCM8t5K05z5ixStDkqMSu4X0w_z4aOP8-Gjg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1735524%2Forg%2F76df3a4f202f806f40eef46fa4e63065.jpg%2FV-8wlDtgCM8t5K05z5ixStDkqMSu4X0w_z4aOP8-Gjg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c07325f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>不鏽鋼飲管當然有助推動環保，但客觀而言，當其變成潮流、消費品的時候，不鏽鋼飲的與塑膠飲管同樣會對環境造成不良影響。隨着愈來愈多消費者購買不鏽鋼飲管，而不鏽鋼飲管又屬消耗品，不能永久使用（也有清潔困難的問題，須以其他工具輔助清潔），<span style=\"color: red;\">這變相便是製造出多幾件垃圾。若一方面打着保護環境的旗號，另一方面又繼續鼓吹綠色消費主義，豈不是予人「偽善」的感覺嗎</span>？</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/sport/2018/09/20180920_straw_4-e1537421937343.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsport%2F2018%2F09%2F20180920_straw_4-e1537421937343.jpeg&h=484c8299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紙飲管咪又係要斬樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔耐少少仲會變軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係一樣咁唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2110000/2110964/sugarcanestraw_180527_0006_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2110000%2F2110964%2Fsugarcanestraw_180527_0006_1024.jpg&h=f13e6dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>台灣近日成功研發一款可自然分解的甘蔗纖維飲管，更可用來喝珍珠奶茶。（照片來源：「100%植」網站）</em></span><br />\n<em>團隊想到用植物纖維取代塑膠，成為製作飲管的原料，經過<ins>反覆試驗</ins>，團隊終於本年5月成功研發出可重複使用，能於泥土自然分解的甘蔗纖維飲管，不會對環境帶來負擔。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀點解整支飲管要晒咁多心機同埋時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有冇人諗過其實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>通菜</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/640pix/20060605/Article_LiveMag/05fqk36p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20060605%2FArticle_LiveMag%2F05fqk36p.jpg&h=44463ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">長通粉</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/84/Rigatoni.jpg/220px-Rigatoni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F84%2FRigatoni.jpg%2F220px-Rigatoni.jpg&h=b0fb4923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解無人諗到呢兩樣食物<br />\n可以做飲管之餘<br />\n飲完嘢可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>食返落肚</strong></span>或者當係廚餘咁處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">慳錢之餘又環保！</div></span></span><br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求理性討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e19cf464e85381ea760edf234353034a6852c0","tid":869646,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f95e79e2f4c5de4024a0b935d657fc89251aca8","tid":869646,"uid":199902,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"廁紙筒"},{"pid":"fd259c88a7d5ca930f935fa0064c25d7f0c642ec","tid":869646,"uid":198810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3f95e79e2f4c5de4024a0b935d657fc89251aca8","tid":869646,"uid":199902,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"廁紙筒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"巴打好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dea8f7aa9726437cadefd6a3c73c711cd943ef","tid":869646,"uid":127726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"植物都有生命嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img